comments:
Abolished 1.4.1934 and divided between the parishes of Aberporth, 
    Llandygwydd and Bettws Evan. See also Table 2, note (b).
Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Llangoedmore.
Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Verwig.

In 1889 the part of the parish of St. Dogmells in Cardigan Municipal 
    Borough became part of Cardiganshire, in 1894 this area became the separate 
    parish of St. Dogmells Municipal and the remaining portion in Cardiganshire 
    of St. Dogmells became the parish of St. Dogmells Rural.
Abolished 1.10.1933 and added to the parish of Cardigan.

Abolished 1.4.1934 and divided between the parishes of Verwig and 
    Llangoedmore.
Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Verwig.
